text.tspan: Place a SINGLE PIECE of your colour on top of a TOWER
whose top piece is a different colour and is the same size or larger
Where a TOWER whose top piece is not your colour contains 2 or more
pieces of your colour, remove 1 and place as a SINGLE PIECE
Where two pieces not of your colour are next to each other in a TOWER,
form a new TOWER with the upper piece and any pieces above it
SETUP: Place all pieces on the board as SINGLE PIECES
